---
title: Spiced Steak Fajitas with Bell Peppers and Tomato Salsa
description: The spiced steak strips in these fajitas are the star of the show. And like any scene-stealer, they outshine the other ingredients inside these tortillas. But if your kids hesitate when given veggies, that might actually be a good thing. Strips of green and yellow peppers and a fresh tomato salsa are snuck in, tucked beneath a cover up of sour cream, and cheddar cheese. You might even be shocked at how fast they gobble it all up.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spiced-steak-fajitas-ddfa5d72.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/spiced-steak-fajitas-10dfed66.pdf
cuisine: North America
servings: 2
